=09=09=09=09America=01,s telecoms giant, AT&T, will be split into four sepa=
rate companies=20
dealing, respectively, with broadband applications, wireless, consumer=20
services and business services, in a bid to enhance shareholder value; AT&T=
=01,s=20
shares had lost 54% this year. The new plan represents an about-turn after=
=20
three years of buying small companies worth a total of $100 billion.
=09=09=09=09See article: AT&T breaks itself up
