 only 26.8=20
trillion lire ($11.6 billion), with the five bidders=01*Omnitel Pronto Ital=
ia,=20
IPSE, Wind, Andala and Telecom Italia Mobile=01*each offering about the sam=
e=20
bid. Following through on an earlier threat, investors in Blu, a consortium=
